Assigned to: Government, Labor, and Elections
Committee Report: Favorable with amendments
House action: Adopted
Read second time: February 22, 2026
CHAPTER ______
1 AN ACT concerning
2 Election Law – Presidential Electors – Selection and Voting
3 FOR the purpose of altering the procedures for the selection of presidential elector
4 nominees and alternate presidential elector nominees; requiring the State
5 Administrator of Elections to preside and serve as secretary at a certain meeting of
6 certain presidential electors; altering the procedures for the meeting of presidential
7 electors; establishing procedures for the preparation, delivery, signing, and
8 transmission of an amended certificate of ascertainment after the vote of the State’s
9 presidential electors under certain circumstances; and generally relating to
10 presidential electors.
11 BY repealing
12 Article – Election Law
13 Section 8–503 through 8–505
