15 STATE’S PRESIDENTIAL ELECTORS AND STATE IN THE CERTIFICATE THAT:
16 (1) THE PRESIDENTIAL ELECTORS WILL SERVE AS PRESIDENTIAL
17 ELECTORS UNLESS A VACANCY OCCURS IN THE OFFICE OF PRESIDENTIAL ELECTOR
18 BEFORE THE END OF THE MEETING AT WHICH PRESIDENTIAL ELECTOR VOTES ARE
19 CAST, IN WHICH CASE A SUBSTITUTE PRESIDENTIAL ELECTOR WILL FILL THE
20 VACANCY; AND
21 (2) IF A SUBSTITUTE PRESIDENTIAL ELECTOR IS APPOINTED TO FILL
22 A VACANCY, THE GOVERNOR WILL SUBMIT AN AMENDED CERTIFICATE OF
23 ASCERTAINMENT STATING THE NAMES ON THE FINAL LIST OF THE PRESIDENTIAL
24 ELECTORS.
25 8–507.
26 (A) THE STATE ADMINISTRATOR SHALL PRESIDE AND SERVE AS
